dct_title_s: Pennsauken Township, Camden County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map covers the area from Delair Avenue to Bannard Avenue along Delaware River. Map shows the various numbered properties in Pennsauken Township. Six of the numbered properties have corresponding owners on the key in the upper left corner.
